Package: kfltCNV
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-01-08
Title: kfltCNV: A tool for calling CNV (Copy number variations) by the Kalman Filter
Author: Qi-Yuan Li, 
    Zhan-Ni Chen
Maintainer: Zhan-Ni Chen <sanadamakomi@gmail.com>
